http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/karnataka/Zilla-panchayat-chief-CEO-cycle-to-work/article13995007.ece

President of Mysuru Zilla Panchayat Pushpavathi Amarnath arrived on a bicycle to the KDP meeting, along with Chairman of the Standing Committee Javare Gowda, here on Monday.The officials opted to pedal in a bid to spread awareness on the environment.Chief Executive Officer of the zilla panchayat P.A. Gopal arrived in a battery-operated scooter. Ms. Amarnath had given a call to officials to come to the meeting on bicycles. However, many failed to do so. At the meeting, she urged officials again to use bicycles and avoid scooters or cars to protect the earth. Using motor vehicles will have a debilitating effect on the environment, she said.